{"type": "article", "id": 29916, "title": "Oscar de la Renta 创意总监离职，以及，推荐一组日常装｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-21T03:49:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1097, "name": "百货"}, {"id": 7561, "name": "18K 金"}, {"id": 18072, "name": "创意总监"}, {"id": 30438, "name": "领导层‘"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 1581, "name": "Chloe"}, {"id": 3659, "name": "Oscar de la Renta"}, {"id": 8413, "name": "Jo Malone"}, {"id": 14728, "name": "Helmut Lang"}, {"id": 20048, "name": "Nordstrom"}, {"id": 30439, "name": "悦木之源"}, {"id": 4703, "name": "刘雯"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607211037303FthCbqkBriO6m2e.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/peter-copping-exits-oscar-de-la-renta-inc-creative-director-10493801/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Oscar de la Renta 创意总监离职</b></a>｜Oscar de la Renta 任职期将近两年的创意总监 Peter Copping 周三宣布离职，周三晚发布的声明中表示因个人原因将离开纽约、回到欧洲。Copping 是继 2014 年创始人 Oscar de la Renta 逝世后首位掌管品牌的设计师。</p><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Nordstrom-names-Scott-Meden-and-Kristin-Frossmo-to-executive-roles,715215.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Nordstrom 任命两位新高管</b></a>｜Nordstrom 百货公司近日宣布 Scott Meden 担任执行副总裁及首席营销官，Kristin Frossmo 担任鞋履部门执行副总裁。Meden 于 2006 年 2 月起就在 Nordstrom 担任高级副总裁职位，而 Frossmo 在 Nordstrom 已有近 30 年，最近刚升任女装部门分销经理。</p><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Estee-Lauder-makes-executive-leadership-changes,715622.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雅诗兰黛领导层变动</b></a>｜雅诗兰黛集团近日宣布旗下品牌 Jo Malone 和 Origins 的高层变动，其中 Jean-Guillaume Trottier 升任 Jo Malone London 全球品牌总裁，Julie Van Ongevalle 则成为 Origins 的全球总经理及高级副总裁。Trottier 从 2012 年起开始担任 Jo Malone 的全球总经理，在他的领导下，品牌销售额翻倍，且成功在巴西、韩国、中国、以色列等地区发布。Ongevalle  2004 年以倩碧市场总监身份加入雅诗兰黛集团。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/menswear-news/designer-luxury/axel-arigato-small-leather-goods-10493399/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>球鞋品牌 Axel Arigato 将推出配件系列</b></a>｜<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/16756.html\">此前我们报道过一个新晋流行瑞典球鞋品牌 Axel Arigato</a> ，即将发布配件系列。包括粒面皮革制的拉链钱包和卡包，上半部出现金色品牌 logo。价格在 40 镑至 65 镑美元之间，预计 7 月 21 日上市。</p><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721092456YdBuLc84VotzmU60.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>法国奢侈品牌 Chloé 推出 <a href=\"http://www.buro247.me/fashion/accessories/chlo-introduces-their-newly-redefined-carolina-sun.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">18K 金 Carlina 系列太阳镜</a>，全球限量 600 副。8 月起在 Chloé 精品店发售：</p><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721095952C9qPSlDbWaOUf7i4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721100000ZgGmLNaR8rivxpT3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721100000KBW7UOQj0Jxd8NVC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721100007w2i5DltH8I3sWSbm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p>adidas 与设计师 Stella McCartney 的联名系列又推出秋冬新款，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/karlie-kloss-is-the-new-face-of-adidas-by-stella-mccartney/\" rel=\"nofollow\">超模 Karlie Kloss 拍摄广告</a>：</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607210849088G6va5P1nuNdorL9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721084908WVmJPLxzl1w9D3gv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721084908bT1EIWcJAm3Rr5Mk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721084908oGmcnTWPzXpRytK6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/helmut-lang-spring-summer-2017-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Helmut Lang 的 2017 春季系列</a>，为高端时装注入更多运动休闲元素：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721100251rQqj1TxtF5R9pML8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607211002525wRHpDST7j0oJUlA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721100256ZjyauGOVLA8EPlwB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721100257wQ4JPhx3NlLrpRb6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721100257twD9eac0bL4l53Or.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721100258xbL8yuPgBIRfZ7wA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721100258M8CGL5gaZlbnFQmr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607211002584bhPoEc08A1BOdTI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">精品店 <a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/07/20/need-supply-nsco-capsule/#slide-13\" rel=\"nofollow\">Need Supply Co. 推出了一个以日式风格的胶囊系列</a>：<br></p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721101841OAGi82R6quKSzv0C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.729662\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721101841KXcvxkDQ3L8ndT1y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.729662\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721101841C0LrKVIWlmwU9gAH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.729662\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721101842rUaVi1Cnxc7zI68t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.729662\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721101842fWAgLiPhJ2v5q38n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.729662\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607211018424rTatfKzAdNeXpL9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.729662\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.buro247.me/fashion/buro-loves/first-look-giorgio-armani-s-autumn-winter-16-campa.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Giorgio Armani 发布秋季最新黑白色调广告大片</a>：<br></p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607211005437zsOAydYRGPeScEa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721100544rjwcRF2ay5de8oVE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721100545PH4BWQmnMy9N8Vht.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.683801\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721100546IoYtXN0RaCZQnAFp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.683801\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashion-press.net/news/gallery/24870/432122\" rel=\"nofollow\">NARS 发布全新秋冬系列彩妆</a>，包含腮红、修容、唇笔和眼线笔等：<br></p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607210940189POKfCtbFIuyUvjM.jpg\"